WEBVTT

00:01:58.629 --> 00:02:01.261
Ko'plik shaklini yasashda eski

00:02:01.261 --> 00:02:02.377
ingliz tilida -s dan

00:02:02.377 --> 00:02:04.111
boshqa qo'shimchalar ham bo'lgan.

00:02:04.111 --> 00:02:06.726
'Child' ning ko'pligi 'children' 
bo'lganidek,

00:02:06.726 --> 00:02:09.451
bitta qo'zichoq 'lamb', ko'pi 'lambru',

00:02:09.451 --> 00:02:11.618
bitta tuxum 'egg', ko'pi 'eggru'

00:02:11.618 --> 00:02:13.288
va bir nechta non 'breads' emas,

00:02:13.288 --> 00:02:15.070
'breadru' bo'lgan bo'lar edi.

00:02:15.070 --> 00:02:17.084
Ba'zi so'zlar ko'plikda umuman
o'zgarmagan,

00:02:17.084 --> 00:02:19.741
masalan, zamonaviy so'z "qo'y"ni 
keltirsak — bitta qo'y

00:02:19.741 --> 00:02:20.617
— 'sheep',

00:02:20.617 --> 00:02:21.742
ko'p qo'y — 'sheep'.

00:02:21.742 --> 00:02:22.829
Qadimgi ingliz tilida

00:02:22.829 --> 00:02:24.612
uy — 'house',
ko'p uylar — 'house'.

00:02:24.612 --> 00:02:28.704
Bugungi kunda "ho'kizlar" so'zi 'oxes' 
emas, 'oxen' bo'lganidek,

00:02:28.704 --> 00:02:32.199
qadimgi insonlar tillar 'tonguen',